33:51.681 --> 33:53.335
Thank you.

33:53.466 --> 33:54.858
Thank you.

33:55.033 --> 33:56.425
Yeah. I got this, okay?

33:56.599 --> 33:58.079
All right.Go.

33:58.253 --> 33:59.211
Yeah.

34:10.744 --> 34:12.137
[quietly]:Come in.

