attention on you. Trust me.

34:49.609 --> 34:51.393
He say something to you?

34:51.567 --> 34:53.395
Well, he doesn't talk to me,

34:53.569 --> 34:56.268
but between us, he's not happy.

34:56.398 --> 34:57.617
I heard
he saw the news coverage.

35:00.010 --> 35:02.230
Well, give me your phone.

35:02.404 --> 35:03.623
You don't want this
to trace back to you.

35:03.797 --> 35:05.233
I'll-I'll wipe it for you.

35:10.499 --> 35:12.197
All right, I got it.

35:13.502 --> 35:15.287
