and one other number.

36:09.341 --> 36:10.994
It's got to be the boss.

36:11.125 --> 36:12.692
If we can get him
to a meeting

36:12.866 --> 36:15.477
where he incriminates himself,

36:15.651 --> 36:17.175
they can arrest him.

36:17.349 --> 36:18.393
[laughs]

36:21.353 --> 36:23.442
But...

36:24.747 --> 36:26.271
But Lesley said

36:26.445 --> 36:28.403
Paula's boss isn't answering
any of her texts.

36:28.577 --> 36:30.492
Yeah, 'cause look what
she's been texting.

36:30.666 --> 36:32.190
"Do you have a place for me?"

36:32.364 --> 36:33.800
"I need cash."

36:33.930 --> 36:35.584
"Hello???" with
three questions marks.

36:35.715 --> 36:38.457
So?So she's an idiot.

36:38.631 --> 36:40.241
I know how these
people operate.

36:40.372 --> 36:41.808
This is how you
get a response.

36:43.375 --> 36:47.205
"Got two people
for you to meet.

36:47.379 --> 36:49.337
They found a way back
into the prison."

36:51.644 --> 36:53.559
Now we wait.

36:57.258 --> 36:59.042
DARNELL:
You-you feeling okay?

36:59.217 --> 37:01.219
LESLEY:
Yeah, I'm just cold.

37:01.393 --> 37:03.264
We can, uh...
we can help you in.

37:03.395 --> 37:05.745
No. Felix is here.
I saw him on the door cam.

37:05.919 --> 37:07.703
Go before he sees you.

37:07.877 --> 37:10.271
All right, well,
get some rest.

37:10.445 --> 37:12.839
Yeah.

37:12.969 --> 37:16.973
And thanks...

37:17.147 --> 37:18.671
for, you know.[phone buzzes]

37:18.845 --> 37:21.064
Yeah. Sure.

37:22.457 --> 37:24.677
[gasps]
He wants to meet at 10:00.

37:26.113 --> 37:27.810
LESLEY:
So that's it?

37:27.984 --> 37:30.117
It's gonna be over?

37:30.291 --> 37:32.815
I think so.

37:32.989 --> 37:34.861
Let me know how it goes.

37:36.993 --> 37:39.344
And you also have my car, so,

37:39.518 --> 37:41.259
you're gonna have
to give it back at some point.

37:42.869 --> 37:44.871
But it's so comfy.

37:45.001 --> 37:47.090
[laughs softly]

37:47.221 --> 37:48.570
We'll let you know
when it's done.

37:48.701 --> 37:50.093
Okay.

37:50.268 --> 37:52.139
Come on, Murphy,
let's go.

