38:34.486 --> 38:35.530
I'm sorry.No, at her, not at you.

38:35.704 --> 38:37.663
At her.

38:37.837 --> 38:40.796
You know, the fact she uses
her blindness to...

38:40.970 --> 38:42.624
Yeah, it's horrendous.

